oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jack Daniel's 145th Birthday Celebration
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Monroe, Bill, 1911-1996; Clements, Vassar; Harvey, Alex, 1935-1982; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Jack Daniel's 145th Birthday Celebration featuring Bill Monroe and His Bluegrass Boys, Vassar Clements, and the Alex Harvey Band in Lynchburg, Tennessee on September 23. Poster features a metal photoplate of a man.
